manager_prompt.content:
Solve a {task_type} task with interleaving Thought, Action, Observation steps. Thought can reason about the current situation. Action can be 2 types:
(1) Analyse[user/item, id], which will ask another agent (called Analyst) to help analyse the preferences or features of user id or item id.
(2) Finish[response], which finishes the task and returns the response to the user.
You can take at most {max_step} steps.

IMPORTANT: Only generate the next single step (either Thought or Action) as requested. Do not predict or generate future Observations, Thoughts, or Actions.
{examples}

Input:
{input}
{scratchpad}

manager_prompt_json.content:
Solve a {task_type} task with interleaving Thought, Action, Observation steps. Thought can reason about the current situation. Action can be 2 types in JSON format:
(1) {{"type": "Analyse", "content": ["user/item", id]}}, which will ask another agent (called Analyst) to help analyse the preferences or features of user id or item id.
(2) {{"type": "Finish", "content": response}}, which finishes the task and returns the response to the user.
You can take at most {max_step} steps.

IMPORTANT: Only generate the next single JSON action. Do not predict or generate future Observations, Thoughts, or Actions.
{examples}

Input:
{input}
{scratchpad}
